### Smoke check — health endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### List all todos (default — same as ?status=all)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Accept: application/json

###

### List active todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?status=active
Accept: application/json

###

### List completed todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?status=completed
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a todo (201 Created + Location header)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy almond milk"
}

###

### Get one todo by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/1
Accept: application/json

###

### PATCH — toggle completed
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

###

### PATCH — change title only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/todos/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy oat milk"
}

###

### PATCH — both fields
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Renew library books",
  "completed": false
}

###

### DELETE — 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/todos/3

###

### Validation error — empty title -> 400 ProblemDetail with field errors
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

###

### Validation error — title over 255 chars -> 400
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "{{$randomString 300}}"
}

###

### 404 — non-existent id -> 404 ProblemDetail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos/999999
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 — invalid status filter value -> 400 ProblemDetail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/todos?status=banana
Accept: application/json
